# MGI does not require any environment variables at build or runtime.
#
# The OpenRouter API key is entered by each user inside the app (Settings →
# OpenRouter API Key) and stored on-device in localStorage under
# `mgi:settings:v1`. It is never read from process.env, never sent to a
# Lovable server, and never committed to git.
#
# Leave this file empty. It exists only so contributors know there are no
# hidden secrets required to run the project.
